{"slug": "invoke", "root": "invoke", "category": "act", "gloss": "to call upon a power", "definition": null, "history": null, "def_sources": [], "is_keyword": false, "etymology": {"lang": "Latin", "origin": "Latin invocare 'to call upon' (in- + vocare 'to call')", "first": "early 15c.", "note": "The exact opposite of evoke: to invoke is to call a power INTO oneself, to evoke is to call it OUT. Ceremonial magic keeps the distinction precise.", "hook": "Invoke vs evoke: calling in against calling out."}, "essay": null, "sources": ["Etymonline (Douglas Harper)", "Wiktionary", "classical lexica (Lewis & Short, LSJ, Bosworth–Toller)", "Ted's historical-magic DBs (WitchcraftStudiesDB, AgrippaDOP, MedievalMagicDB)"], "stats": {"flavor_total": 3, "oracle_total": 3, "in_flavor_cards": 3, "in_oracle_cards": 3, "name_match_count": 8, "by_variant": {"invoke": 4, "invoking": 1, "invoked": 1}, "first_year": 1994, "colors": {"U": 5, "R": 3, "W": 2, "G": 1, "B": 2}, "by_year": {"1994": 1, "2012": 1, "2017": 1, "2021": 2, "2022": 5, "2024": 1, "2026": 1}}, "cards": [{"id": "5b3f041e-ad4a-47ea-bdc4-1be2353f2e18", "name": "Invoke Calamity", "set": "NEO", "type_line": "Instant", "rarity": "rare", "colors": ["R"], "img_small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/f/e/fe666c86-6734-4c47-9244-bcd26b54068d.jpg?1782702234", "img_normal": "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/f/e/fe666c86-6734-4c47-9244-bcd26b54068d.jpg?1782702234", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/neo/147/invoke-calamity?utm_source=api", "local": "img/invoke/5b3f041e-ad4a-47ea-bdc4-1be2353f2e18.jpg"}, {"id": "f9ee4c80-20fb-4322-be02-1c78d37d7a99", "name": "Invoke Despair", "set": "NEO", "type_line": "Sorcery", "rarity": "rare", "colors": ["B"], "img_small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/3/5/35af9d5c-4449-4549-b549-c3ba4a67dee0.jpg?1782702265", "img_normal": "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/3/5/35af9d5c-4449-4549-b549-c3ba4a67dee0.jpg?1782702265", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/neo/1