5-4ee7-a3c8-beed109a7f38.jpg?1782752155", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/ddj/31/invoke-the-firemind?utm_source=api", "local": "img/invoke/2037659f-2efe-4321-afaf-961bbec35e9e.jpg"}, {"id": "721c3255-953c-49cd-a5dd-852c3d09eae4", "name": "Invoke the Winds", "set": "NEO", "type_line": "Sorcery", "rarity": "rare", "colors": ["U"], "img_small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/a/d/ad7b423a-bfd1-47aa-bd2c-64a169b96924.jpg?1782702292", "img_normal": "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/a/d/ad7b423a-bfd1-47aa-bd2c-64a169b96924.jpg?1782702292", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/neo/58/invoke-the-winds?utm_source=api", "local": "img/invoke/721c3255-953c-49cd-a5dd-852c3d09eae4.jpg"}, {"id": "87bd0fdb-c5b9-46ea-9858-1a870960351f", "name": "Invoke the Divine", "set": "KHM", "type_line": "Instant", "rarity": "common", "colors": ["W"], "img_small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/7/2/7213d9e1-e9c6-45d8-bb7f-336c41e7b6f7.jpg?1782705541", "img_normal": "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/7/2/7213d9e1-e9c6-45d8-bb7f-336c41e7b6f7.jpg?1782705541", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/khm/16/invoke-the-divine?utm_source=api", "local": "img/invoke/87bd0fdb-c5b9-46ea-9858-1a870960351f.jpg"}], "flavor_snippets": [{"card": "Haunting Hymn", "set": "IMA", "html": "The hymn&#x27;s melody has persisted since Tourach&#x27;s time, but the words changed to <mark>invoke</mark> the phobias of each listener.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/2/b/2be041f3-482d-40f3-a525-39e3d6890c56.jpg?1782748435"}, {"card": "Lightning Strike", "set": "MSH", "html": "<mark>Invoking</mark> Thor&#x27;s wrath is a mistake few villains are stupid enough—or sturdy enough—to make twice.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/8/8/88b13bc0-da54-4c3b-917c-7c8345a329f5.jpg?1782681794"}, {"card": "Quench", "set": "RVR", "html": "&quot;When properly <mark>invoked</mark>, the plasma globule encloses the offensive spell with a satisfying slurp.&quot;", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/1/7/1779a6c5-147d-4632-b1d9-95e89a64dc2c.jpg?1782731175"}], "mechanics_snippets": [{"card": "Trickster's Talisman", "set": "AFR", "html": "<mark>Invoke</mark> Duplicity — Equipped creature gets +1/+1 and has &quot;Whenever this creature deals combat damage to a player, you may sacrifice Trickster&#x27;s Talisman. If you do, create a token that&#x27;s a copy of this creature.&quot;\nEquip {2}"}, {"card": "Invoke the Firemind", "set": "DDJ", "html": "Choose one —\n• Draw X cards.\n• <mark>Invoke</mark> the Firemind deals X damage to any target."}, {"card": "Invoke Calamity", "set": "NEO", "html": "You may cast up to two instant and/or sorcery spells with total mana value 6 or less from your graveyard and/or hand without paying their mana costs. If those spells would be put into your graveyard, exile them instead. Exile <mark>Invoke</mark> Calamity."}], "thumb": {"art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/3/3/33cb9973-c9ce-48f1-9972-651092624751.jpg?1782704395", "small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/3/3/33cb9973-c9ce-48f1-9972-651092624751.jpg?1782704395", "card": "Trickster's Talisman"}}